domain 3d
OutputManager tstep_all dofman_all element_all
ncrosssect 1 nmat 1 nbc 0 nic 0 nltf 1 nset 0
SimpleCS 1 material 1
IsoLE 1 d 1.0 E 30.e9 n 0.2 talpha 0
ConstantFunction 1 f(t) 1.0
